detail.title: Nebulae Upgrade
detail.description:
### RIZON Nebulae Upgrade

This onchain software upgrade, called Nebulae, will add a number of upstream version updates, fixes and new modules, especially enable the CosmWasm.
* By voting YES to this proposal, you approve of adding this upgrade.
* By voting NO to this proposal, you do not approve of this upgrade.

### Informations

* Upgrade name: Nebulae
* Upgrade Block Height: 9522000
* Upgrade Time: around 2023-07-20 08:00 (UTC)

Please see more informations [here](https://github.com/rizon-world/mainnet/blob/master/upgrade/Nebulae.md).

detail.title: Issue RCHF
detail.description:
### Issue RCHF

This is a proposal to issue a stablecoin, RCHF on RIZON Blockchain.

Unlike other stablecoins that fluctuate in price depending on its underlying cryptocurrencies, RCHF is designed to maintain price equivalence to the Switzerland CHF. In order to increase stability and reliability, RCHF coins are guaranteed by fiat currency reserve from Maerki Baumann : private bank in Zürich, Switzerland. RCHF will differentiate from its competitors by implementing the highest level of regulations to secure users' assets. Making it perfect for worldwide payments, capital markets, and global trade.

* Vote YES if you are in favor of issuing RCHF on RIZON blockchain
* Vote NO if you are opposed of issuing RCHF on RIZON blockchain.
